## Current issues

### 1. No global error handling
Express needs an error-handling middleware (4-arg signature) as the last `app.use()` call. Without it, thrown errors leak stack traces to clients in development and silently fail in production.

### 2. No 404 handler
Unknown routes fall through to Express's default, which isn't explicit.

