| Priority | Change | Why |
|---|---|---|
| P0 | Add error-handling middleware + 404 handler | Stack traces / unclear errors leak info |
| P0 | Guard `app.listen` behind `require.main === module` | Breaks tests, double-bind in prod |
| P0 | Add `helmet` | Free, baseline security headers |
| P1 | Add rate limiting | Prevents trivial DoS / credential stuffing later |
| P1 | Validate route params & query with `express-validator` (or `zod`) | Defense in depth as endpoints grow |
| P1 | Remove / gate PII (`email`) behind auth | PII exposure |
| P2 | Body parser `limit` | DoS protection when POST routes are added |
| P2 | Structured logging with redaction | Incident response, avoid logging secrets |
| P2 | Graceful shutdown | Clean deploys, no dropped connections |

