| Priority | Change |
|---|---|
| High | Add 404 + centralized error middleware; stop leaking stack traces |
| High | Add `helmet`, size-limited body parser, explicit CORS allowlist, rate limiting |
| High | Require auth for `/users`; limit returned PII |
