| Priority | Change | Why |
|---|---|---|
| High | Add `helmet` + disable `x-powered-by` | Broad hardening, one line |
| High | Centralized error middleware + stack-trace suppression in prod | Prevent info leakage |
| High | Authenticate `/users` before returning emails | PII exposure |
| High | `express.json({ limit })` | DoS prevention |
| Medium | `express-rate-limit` | Brute-force / scraping mitigation |
| Medium | `express-validator` on every input | Defense in depth |
| Medium | Graceful shutdown + `listen` error callback | Operational resilience |
| Low | `process.env.PORT` | Config flexibility |

