A minimal Express app should include:

- **`helmet`** — sets secure HTTP headers (CSP, HSTS, X-Frame-Options, etc.):
  ```js
  const helmet = require('helmet');
  app.use(helmet());
  ```
- **`cors`** — explicit allowlist instead of default-open:
  ```js
  const cors = require('cors');
  app.use(cors({ origin: ['https://your-frontend.example.com'], methods: ['GET'] }));
