| 7 | Input validation scaffolding (zod/joi) | Medium | Needed before adding any input-taking route |
| 8 | Graceful shutdown | Medium | Important under a real process manager |
| 9 | Structured logging / request IDs | Medium | Forensics |
| 10 | Explicit CORS policy | Low-Medium | Depends on consumer |

